_sText:
Original map posted by F|4THeAd, it was requested that the weapons be changed from deagles to dual elites & thus we get fy_elite.
Screenshots from cs_deagle5
ALL credit should go to F|4THeAd for this map, my only contribution was the weapons change.

cs_deagle5 Notes:

This is a remake by me(F|4THeAd) of the original cs_deagle5 from 1.6. The structure of the map has been kept in tact. Players start with full body armor and a deagle with full ammo. The map does support 16 players on each side, but that could get chaotic.

cs_deagle5 is not a complicated map, but usually simple maps lead to more fun.
